{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-people-page-js","path":"/speakers/deborah-gordon","result":{"data":{"people":{"parent":{"html":"<h2>About</h2>\n<p>Deborah Gordon is a senior principal in the Climate Intelligence Program at <a href=\"https://rmi.org/\">RMI</a> where she leads the Oil and Gas Solutions Initiative. Gordon serves as a senior fellow at the Watson Institute of International and Public Affairs at Brown University and serves as an affiliate at the Climate Solutions Lab. Her research spearheaded the development of the <a href=\"https://ociplus.rmi.org/\">Oil Climate Index Plus Gas</a> (OCI+), a first-of-its-kind analytic tool that compares the life-cycle climate impacts of global oil and gas resources. The OCI+ is the topic of Gordonâ€™s new book, No Standard Oil (Oxford University Press, 2021).</p>"},"id":"7c706c09-0814-550a-8997-2bc46e444393","title":"Deborah Gordon","company":"RMI","role":"Senior Principal","twitter":null,"pronouns":null,"avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/1b50a/deborah-gordon.jpg","srcSet":"/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/c904d/deborah-gordon.jpg 160w,\n/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/b95ad/deborah-gordon.jpg 320w,\n/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/1b50a/deborah-gordon.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/c6aca/deborah-gordon.webp 160w,\n/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/0a0af/deborah-gordon.webp 320w,\n/static/78bfd14e50b073489952929dca0dfec2/8ae69/deborah-gordon.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":640}}},"events":[{"role":"speakers","event":{"parent":{"html":"<p>NASA has designated 2023 as the Year of Open Science. The shift to shared cloud data and services creates new opportunities for open, 